# Environment Variables (Optional — enables real AI via Google Gemini)

# Get a free API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# Local dev: create .env in project root with the line above, then restart `npm run dev`
# Vercel: Settings → Environment Variables → add GEMINI_API_KEY for Production

# Do NOT prefix with VITE_ — the key stays server-side via /api/ai
